Extract an multilang MIUI rom and decompile apks, than run prepare_translations_and_copy_to_the_translations_folder.sh
This will copy all strings.xml and folders from multilang to the translations folder,
than you can customise customize_miui_app.sh ...see stock_lotus customize_miui_app.sh for idea!
This is designed to pick multilang strings in comparation with default strings.xml trought prevod.php and make you
ideal translations structure which is the same like default strings.xml but translated. Than your apk will contain
all translations which is the same like in multilang but modified to look like default strings.xml...
